                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310217-217-victim2035 t18310217-217-viclabel1272"></join> at No. 9, Great Warner-street. These scales are hers - I used them about three minutes before they were missed.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. The other <rs id="t18310217-217-deflabel1273" type="occupation">boy</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310217-217-defend2033 t18310217-217-deflabel1273"></join> took them, and I did not know of it - he saw them coming, and tried to shove them into my pocket.</p>
